We have a very specific time frame that we can run this meeting.

564
00:57:22,335 --> 00:57:24,777
We have to end at seven o'clock, so we have to kind of keep that in mind.

565
00:57:25,798 --> 00:57:37,644
And I also, my other thought is that, you know, we don't want to just say, hey, well, if we, if we find a need for this in the future, we can amend this, which we could, but it can also be kind of insulting.

566
